Hello, thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Lawrence Mitchell. I'd be happy to help you today. May I have your name, please?

Hi, Lawrence. My name is Carol Bennett.

Nice to meet you, Carol. How can I assist you with our yacht inventory today?

I'm interested in knowing what kinds of yachts you currently have available.

Sure thing. To provide you with the best options, could I ask for your preferred yacht size in feet?

I'm looking for something around forty to fifty feet.

Great, and do you have a specific budget range we should keep in mind for the yachts?

Yes, I'm considering something in the range of three hundred thousand to four hundred thousand dollars.

Thank you for that information, Carol. I will look into our current inventory and get back to you shortly with options that fit your preferences.

Thank you for your time today, Carol. If you have any other questions in the meantime, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
